sub_title: Account Manager France | Seasons Decoration | Retail advice
summary:
Pro-active, customer focused and organised person with excellent multilingual skills and extended experience in sales and operational functions. I have more than 17 years of experience within different sales and marketing positions which has given me the opportunity to develop strong knowledge of the selling process and also how to approach each market according to its own culture and specifications. 
Professionalism, service minded, goal orientated and accuracy are some of the characteristics to describe my personality. I have proven to be motivated and to be a good team player. I have personal affinity working in an international and dynamic environment. Moreover, I have an international profile as I am a native French speaker with excellent English, Dutch, Italian and Spanish communication skills.
